{"lastModified":1765830292036,"uri":"c::18230663260::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nBali 4.6 built in 2023, has four double cabins, one bunkbed with 2 single beds and two single cabins outside for the crew, four bathrooms and one smaller bathroom for the crew outside and saloon can turn in to a double bed. Can accommodate up to 12 guests\n\nBali 4.6 combines modular front and aft cockpits, a complete cooking area at the back, a practical and safe access to the sea, still giving Nautal Design large volumes in the salon to fully express themselves. With its double access, the Flybridge is dedicated both to maneuvering and relaxing. Helm station offers protection and visibility.  With two Yanmar engines of 57 HP with turbo for quick navigation and greater maneuvering in the harbor.\n\nOffers every comfort, including:\nAir-condition, Generator, water maker, 2 electric refrigerators, freezer, sink and fridge outside, rib dinghy, mp3 player audio system with Bluetooth and auxiliary port, heater with hot water, electric toilets, 6 hp outboard engine. 800 liters of water and 1000 Liters of Diesel","blueprint":{"name":"ENMA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::7852ec90-2c58-11f0-849f-779b45ba299a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::aa7a2b10-2c59-11f0-9a82-fde7d74cd6fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::aa7aa040-2c59-11f0-9a82-fde7d74cd6fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::aa7b3c80-2c59-11f0-9a82-fde7d74cd6fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::aa7c4df0-2c59-11f0-9a82-fde7d74cd6fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::66e7f140-2c39-11f0-8e72-4980cba9db5a::assets::78413950-2c58-11f0-849f-7